name: A faint realness, rather than outright fake
description: By Travis LeRoy Southworth | @travisleroy | “A faint realness, rather than outright fake” (2021), 2550 x 3000px. This digital painting is part of my series "Thresholds" where I create works partly through a GAN and my own computerized brush strokes. I use the word 'threshold' for my series as it can be a boundary or a starting point of an experience. They are meant to exist on the border between color field and abstract portrait.
